com.langtoun.oastypes

Interface OASArrayType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OASType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OASArrayTypeImpl

    public interface OASArrayType
extends OASType
    Public interface for OpenAPI specification array types. Objects of this type are derived from YAML like this: 
    
   type: array
   items: ...
